/*
**将等级按照海尔规定优化映射
**71-99 不做映射，
**1-49不做映射
**50-70映射成49
*/

uint8_t mappingDegree(uint8_t degree)
{
  //float temp;
  uint8_t degree_out;
  if((degree>=71)||(degree<=49)){//71-99以及1-49之间不做映射
  	degree_out=degree;
  }else {//50~70之间输出49
    degree_out=49;
  }
  //合法区间保护
  if(degree_out>99){
	  degree_out=99;
  }
  if(degree_out<1){
	  degree_out=1;
  }
  return degree_out;
}

uint8_t dataXorCRC(uint8_t * sd,uint8_t length)
{
  uint8_t xordata,i;
  xordata = sd[0];
  for(i=1;i<length;i++)
  {
     xordata ^=sd[i];
  }
  return xordata;
}

